        "gopop02",
        "gopop03",
        "gopop04"
      ],
      "body": "[gopop.co](http://gopop.co)\n\nGoPop is a completely new way to speak in GIFs, photos, videos and drawings. Featured by Apple as a “Best New App,” and Mashable has called GoPop an “app not to miss.” Backed by Lowercase Capital, Advancit Capital, SV Angel, Matter Ventures and the Knight Enterprise Fund.\n\nReleased in February 2014, Joseph was Head Product Architect of the iOS app GoPop. Designing the UI/UX as well as the underlying code for the iOS code in both Objective-C and more recently Swift."
    },
