      "body": "Experiments with ephemeral physical media. Hacked thermal printers to do unexpected things like respond to a phone call or text, tell fortunes, invite you to meet someone at a party, print out a map, or become a makeshift photobooth.\n\nCustom Java library for sending commands to thermal printers written and open-sourced available on [github](https://github.com/jbergen/ESCPos-library)"
