      "body": "An existing website for GTECTS Architects was augmented by a live webcam feed from inside the office in Manhattan. The ultra-portable webcam is repositioned as desired and can broadcast passers by on the sidewalk, or placed inside a working model. The live feed challenges the notion of digital space and presence that has become too familiar in our everyday virtual interactions.\n\nCommissioned by Gordon Kipping of GTECTS"
